  Traits: 
  Prerequisites: []
  Description: You gain nourishment in the same way that the plants or fungi that
    match your body type normally do, through some combination of photosynthesis,
    absorbing minerals with your roots, or scavenging decaying matter. You typically
    do not need to pay for food. If you normally rely on photosynthesis and go without
    sunlight for 1 week, you begin to starve. You can derive nourishment from specially
    formulated bottles of sunlight instead of natural sunlight, but these bottles
    cost 10 times as much as standard rations (or 40 sp).
